== Read the book
You can read the book online from:

https://github.com/Ruk33/a-short-pocket-hand-guide-notes-on-how-to-write-good-code/blob/master/book.pdf

Or download it:

PDF  : https://github.com/Ruk33/a-short-pocket-hand-guide-notes-on-how-to-write-good-code/raw/master/book.pdf
HTML : https://github.com/Ruk33/a-short-pocket-hand-guide-notes-on-how-to-write-good-code/raw/master/book.html

== Requirements
This project uses Pandoc [1] and Docker [2]
to generate PDF and HTML from book.md.

[1]: https://pandoc.org
[2]: https://www.docker.com

== Generate HTML from book
To generate HTML from the book.md file, use:

make book.html

== Generate PDF from book
To generate PDF from the book.md file, use:

make book.pdf

== Clean
To remove the generated PDF and HTML from book.md, use:

make clean

== Push changes
To push new changes in the GIT repository, use

git add .
git commit -m "Your changes"
make push

This will make sure both, PDF and HTML are generated
and pushed to the repository as well.